Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.63,0:00:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,德文\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Devon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.97,0:00:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不 听着 我们不开心 我们很痛苦\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}No. Listen, we're not happy, we're miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.68,0:00:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,伯特\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Burt!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.77,0:00:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们在地下折磨我们 - 德文\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}- They torture us down there! - Devon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.23,0:00:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都是囚犯\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}We're prisoners!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.52,0:00:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,伯特\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Burt!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.94,0:00:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,她还活着\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}She's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.20,0:00:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是 好的 - 好\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Yeah. Okay. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,马克 来 你能抱她一会儿吗\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mark? Here. Will you take her for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.24,0:00:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别担心 我会看着她 好的 - 小心点\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}- It's okay. I got her. Yeah. - Be careful with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.45,0:00:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但别走太远了 - 不会的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Don't go far though. - I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,马克\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.67,0:00:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,所以现在是你吗\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}So, this is you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.01,0:00:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.01,0:00:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.72,0:00:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.51,0:00:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你确定  - 是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Are you sure? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.64,0:01:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫什么\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}What's my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.69,0:01:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,波瑟芬妮\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Persephone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.23,0:01:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你能拼出来吗\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Can you spell that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.86,0:01:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不可能 - 好的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Never. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.53,0:01:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,宝贝\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Babe...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.36,0:01:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的 - ...帮我弄弄尿布\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Okay. - ...need help with this diaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.32,0:01:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.28,0:01:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得她想要妈咪了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}I think she wants mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,恶心的娃\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Fetid moppet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.55,0:02:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.65,0:02:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会派分离层的人员 与员工外面的自己联络\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}We'll have someone from the floor liaise with the outies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.28,0:02:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须查出他们和谁聊过 越快越好\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}We need to find out who they talked to. Promptly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.79,0:03:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须找到他们所有人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}I need you to go see all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.45,0:03:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,查清他们说过什么话 和谁说的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Find out every word they said and who they said it to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.29,0:03:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,要辞退他们吗\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}And shall I fire them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,让基尔为你指引方向\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Let Kier guide your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.34,0:03:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.88,0:04:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,请坐\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Please, sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.68,0:04:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已没收宾客拍摄的视频\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}We've commandeered the footage taken by guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,娜塔莉已经开始与媒体沟通\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Natalie is already doing outreach to media.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.85,0:04:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正在处理涉及此事的分离层员工\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}And the severed employees who were involved are being dealt with.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你的快速应对\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Thank you for acting so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.07,0:04:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你帮我们避免了灾难\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}You saved us from disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.78,0:04:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,伊根先生会加入吗\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Will Mr. Eagan be joining?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.79,0:04:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,只有我\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我本人也应向你表示感谢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}I personally owe you a debt of gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.59,0:05:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我为此付出了极大的代价\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}It cost me dearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,的确\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}It did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管如此 你在今晚证明了 自己对公司的忠诚\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}And still, you proved your loyalty tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,因此我们想重新聘请你\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Which is why we'd like to ask you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.11,0:05:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你们应该道歉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}An apology is warranted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我向你道歉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.62,0:05:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我的父亲向你道歉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}My father apologizes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.09,0:05:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,董事会向你道歉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Board apologizes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.72,0:05:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们对待你非常不公\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}We've treated you poorly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.34,0:05:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:05:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我接受你的道歉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}I welcome your contrition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那太好了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.49,0:06:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,还有许多影响需要消除\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}There's much damage to control.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我建议从源头开始着手调查\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}I recommend we start by scouring the feed,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.91,0:06:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要对迪伦G问话 看看他是如何获得进入...\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}and I need to interview Dylan G. to see how he gained access to the--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在考虑另一件事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}We have something else in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.00,0:06:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想向你提供升职的机会\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}We'd like to offer you a promotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.80,0:06:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,分离顾问委员会\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Severance Advisory Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我从没听过这种组织\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}I never heard of such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.03,0:06:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这是全新的安排 你将领头创建这一委员会\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's a brand-new initiative. You'd be spearheading its formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,公司非常重视你的才干\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Your expertise is greatly valued.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,所以应该由我担任分离层的主管\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Which is why I should be running the severed floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.89,0:07:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,米尔奇克先生已经升职为分离层经理\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mr. Milchick has been promoted to floor manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.56,0:07:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你们不器重我\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}You don't value me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.28,0:07:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你们惧怕我\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}You fear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不惧怕任何人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}We fear no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.87,0:07:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,(治愈全人类的良药)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,正因为我们如此看重你\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}And if we didn't hold you in such high esteem,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.25,0:07:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才会慷慨地向你提供这个机会\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}we wouldn't be making this generous offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.22,0:07:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我会考虑考虑的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'll put some thought to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.19,0:08:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你抽空过来 哈蒙妮 达蒙德先生将送你出去\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Thank you for coming in, Harmony. Mr. Drummond will see you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要别人护送\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}I don't need an escort.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.61,0:08:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,今天傍晚\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Earlier this evening,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.70,0:08:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,在一个晚宴上 我怀着激动的心情 作为已分离员工\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}at an event where I was excited to share my status as a severed individual
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.20,0:09:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,与朋友和合作伙伴们分享我的经历\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}with a group of friends and allies,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但我大意之下在发言前喝了酒\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}I made the poor decision to consume alcohol
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.08,0:09:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,且此前因为手臂起红疹 曾服用非卢蒙制的药物\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}while on a non-Lumon medication for an arm rash.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.42,0:09:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这导致我陷入酩酊状态\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}This had an inebriating effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.75,0:09:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,继而发表了令我深感后悔的言论\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}which caused me to say some deeply regrettable things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 米尔奇克先生 - 抱歉我这么晚才来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Mr. Milchick. - Apologies for the hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,一切还好吗\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Is everything all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.52,0:09:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你今晚过得怎么样 贝立夫先生\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}How's your night been, Mr. Bailiff?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,挺好的 电视上正在播 《塞维利亚的理发师》\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Fine. They're showing Barber of Seville on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我正在家里看\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}So I've just been here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.98,0:09:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,真好 你感觉好吗\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Wonderful. And you're feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.11,0:09:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 我吃了什么\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh, God. What did I eat in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.37,0:09:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只想知道有没有发生什么不寻常的事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}We just need to know if anything of note occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.50,0:09:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,任何事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.87,0:09:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,米尔奇克先生 不如你说说 发生了什么事吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Why don't you tell me what's going on, Mr. Milchick?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.46,0:09:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,当时 我以为自己很幽默\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}In the moment, I thought I was being funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.30,0:09:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但在鲁莽的发言之后\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}But in the hours since this outburst,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我想起我家族的公司\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}I've been reminded just how seriously my family's company
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.39,0:10:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,在世界各地人民的生活中 有多么深远的影响\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}affects the lives of real people around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.94,0:10:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道 你公司里的自己和我是朋友\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}You know, your innie is a friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.15,0:10:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信他也会同意我这么说的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}I feel confident he'd approve of me saying so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他是一个有原则的人 这很难得\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}And he's a man of principle, which is rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.66,0:10:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,所以这真的是一个艰难的决定\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}Which is what makes this so difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你要辞退我\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}You're firing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.17,0:10:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,卢蒙遇到问题时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}When Lumon falters,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,总是我们最珍惜的员工 和他们的家人首当其冲受伤害\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}it's our cherished workers and their families who suffer first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.09,0:10:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,对于这所造成的恐惧和不安 我深切致歉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}So for the fear and insecurity this has caused, I must sincerely atone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.26,0:10:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你在今天傍晚\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs15\1c&H3CF1F3&}You were involved in a physical altercation
